{"generated": "2026-07-16 22:09", "brief": "<b>1. 금융당국의 단일종목 레버리지 ETF 규제 강화</b>\n금융당국이 단일종목 레버리지 ETF에 대한 규제를 대폭 강화하며 시장에 큰 영향을 미치고 있습니다. 신규 상장이 중단되고, 기존 상품에 대한 예탁금도 현금 3천만원으로 상향 조정되어 소액 투자자들의 접근성이 제한될 것으로 보입니다. [<a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiiwFBVV95cUxQNnFqZzdpdUJpUlo4T0M3SUhJRnVJZjdaT0ZUQjFXcUtjUU1BNVZkYUMtenFQZXd1dEY5LXQtZ3JNR3hGcWJ4OG5OakZIMXVMQlU2UGZVUFA4aFhvZmo2cUwzbnQ5eG9lSk4tUlRLTlBDcm9nNnp3bk9MNWhycVA3aDk0R0xFZGtYam9F?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">#7</a> <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiiwFBVV95cUxPSV9CSjdoU1E5TjVmc1N2QWtvQy1ocjZqSTFaMDhLQWc1ZE1LZ0llTzNBQldPTmhGdEp5RTlZQV9zdWJkS29YTU8xUTY4MlI4ZGN3TUZsSGdRVE5naklmYkd2bVVJNU9sbmlnTUs3dktoTWVpS1Q3djhEdjJyVHBRVkRBd2sxeWFEZ0hJ?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">#8</a> <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiZ0FVX3lxTE10VUo0MmNrRWRtRWlpOVV1ckViZkhyZDZpVG1Kd1U0ai02TFRkUU5Ja0xadXdxTzA4OElibk50alNyc3c5OHVCX2dhdVA5UEluYk9ZZGNJS2VzVGhUQmxSYXBHNmdmcTg?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">#20</a> <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiUkFVX3lxTE83bTRGUDlicGFJa0tKUkpyQmZKNUZwZkl5bDFCWmk0N1BJSWJCXzQxWFVodmZGQW5MOEw5ejZrRXh6eWNZVTZwVkVGYzRnbXRFZWc?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">#21</a> <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiXkFVX3lxTE11NFU5NExHNzBORkNpbWNpVEZjSFEzY0l2c1lZM3laTjJhUHhLQlM0NWlQZjdvOEsydGlIMlExNjZ4QXQ0Y2xzelFsdmdJVDI5bjBmVmlSZ05wYUR3d2fSAWNBVV95cUxQTExtZFlIclVUUmNhdmxldDhmQjQyQXZCUEJwSHlmcXlaRFZHU2ZDRVBHMlV2Zm5JTjhGS1RyajVKajl0WXgwclFxNlo2eWpYdklYWXNiYmhnQ2tUMVcxNHFwNWs?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">#25</a> <a href=\"https://news.google.?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">#27</a> <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiT0FVX3lxTE1wTEI2Qkw5Q2RDbWpQNDFuSTVYbFpyN0hXS2xsS2I3ZDhYN2loQXVPTEEzanlKOFRnNXdlMnBiNjFzY1U2b1FDa1NmYjhGaDQ?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">#30</a> <a href=\"https://www.yna.co.kr/view/AKR20260716201700002\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">#33</a